{"tid":2028996,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港維護國家安全法律列附件三　中央可設立相關機構","createTime":"2020-05-22T05:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T05:08:17.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6aaedfd5827d2031adc94f6b710b1e6aad251f47","tid":2028996,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:08:17.000Z","msg":"全國人大會議今早開幕，全國人大副委員長王晨向代表解說其中一項議程，即授權全國人大常委會就建立香港維護國家安全，制定相關法律，防範及懲治任何分裂國家、顛覆國家政權、組織實施恐怖活動、以及外國和境外勢力干預香港特區事務的活動，並將相關法律列入《基本法》附件三，再在香港實施。<br />\n<br />\n文件指出，香港特區應當強化執法力量，中央會根據需要在香港特區設立相關機構。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527681-20200522.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527681-20200522.htm&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzXjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=65032311\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527681-20200522.htm&h=9e9c8bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527681-20200522.htm</a>"}]}